Ma'am, that's ridiculous.

1064
00:59:15,010 --> 00:59:16,853
Well, the police will clarify it with him.

1065
00:59:17,020 --> 00:59:18,110
Police?

1066
00:59:18,540 --> 00:59:21,632
Oh, no, no!
Albert, we can not do that!

1067
00:59:22,496 --> 00:59:24,094
Do not you realize?

1068
00:59:25,234 --> 00:59:29,267
What he knows about me is true.

1069
00:59:30,071 --> 00:59:33,092
I do not dare let him go.

1070
00:59:37,963 --> 00:59:42,870
You have to find another
way to fix this with Karl.

1071
00:59:44,840 --> 00:59:46,115
Sorry Mrs.

1072
00:59:46,905 --> 00:59:49,211
I was wrong to think about my pride.

1073
00:59:49,714 --> 00:59:51,581
There are other things to protect.

1074
00:59:51,582 --> 00:59:53,063
You must be careful.

1075
00:59:53,993 --> 00:59:56,080
A man like that is dangerous.

1076
00:59:56,950 --> 00:59:58,455
I told you, Ma'am.

1077
00:59:58,456 --> 01:00:01,522
I have always been responsible
for the servants of this house.

1078
01:00:02,352 --> 01:00:04,151
I am still responsible.

1079
01:00:05,864 --> 01:00:07,691
And now, if I may...

1080
01:00:08,407 --> 01:00:09,441
Albert.

1081
01:00:11,683 --> 01:00:13,235
About Anna...

1082
01:00:14,619 --> 01:00:15,879
She is young.

1083
01:00:16,748 --> 01:00:19,140
It's not made for a guy like Karl.

1084
01:00:20,350 --> 01:00:22,701
You must be patient with her.

1085
01:00:26,117 --> 01:00:29,029
Women sometimes do nonsense.

1086
01:00:29,899 --> 01:00:32,413
Only because of ignorance.

1087
01:00:34,276 --> 01:00:35,460
Yes.

1088
01:00:35,996 --> 01:00:37,583
Now I see it.

1089
01:02:25,377 --> 01:02:26,383
Between.

1090
01:02:30,365 --> 01:02:31,794
Well thats what you want?

1091
01:02:35,259 --> 01:02:37,199
I'm so miserable.

1092
01:02:38,825 --> 01:02:40,872
You have not talked to me;

1093
01:02:40,873 --> 01:02:42,812
You have not even looked at me.

1094
01:02:42,813 --> 01:02:43,606
Not since...

1095
01:02:43,607 --> 01:02:44,844
Not since you insulted me.

1096
01:02:44,845 --> 01:02:47,136
Oh, Karl! I did not mean that.

1097
01:02:47,425 --> 01:02:50,047
I can not stand it, if
you do not talk to me.

1098
01:02:50,048 --> 01:02:51,717
I do not care what you have done.

1099
01:02:52,296 --> 01:02:53,345
It's okay.

1100
01:02:53,822 --> 01:02:55,164
Do not you care what he has done?

1101
01:02:55,165 --> 01:02:56,038
What have I done?

1102
01:02:56,039 --> 01:02:59,164
I mean you and Anna.

1103
01:02:59,266 --> 01:03:01,457
You will not start with that again!

1104
01:03:01,458 --> 01:03:04,126
More suspicions, more
insults, more reproaches.

1105
01:03:04,127 --> 01:03:07,097
Please, Karl, let's not fight.

1106
01:03:07,574 --> 01:03:09,592
I can not live without you.

1107
01:03:10,302 --> 01:03:12,063
I will do anything.

1108
01:03:13,462 --> 01:03:16,225
If you let me stay here with you.

1109
01:03:18,246 --> 01:03:21,278
For a few days, I would be so happy.

1110
01:03:22,287 --> 01:03:23,287
Karl.

1111
01:03:23,535 --> 01:03:25,304
Karl, let's do what we said.

1112
01:03:26,017 --> 01:03:27,644
Buy a cafeteria.

1113
01:03:28,521 --> 01:03:29,961
With your money?

1114
01:03:30,380 --> 01:03:31,827
It's what you said before.

1115
01:03:31,828 --> 01:03:32,949
Throwing it in my face!

1116
01:03:32,950 --> 01:03:35,390
You think I'm going to give you
another chance to do it again.

1117
01:03:35,818 --> 01:03:37,814
I'm not a sentimental fool.

1118
01:03:38,085 --> 01:03:40,158
It's our money, Karl.

1119
01:03:40,580 --> 01:03:41,654
Look.

1120
01:03:41,655 --> 01:03:43,567
Here it is! All!

1121
01:03:45,275 --> 01:03:47,235
Do you know what is the
saddest thing of all this?

1122
01:03:47,277 --> 01:03:48,915
Just one day before,

1123
01:03:49,308 --> 01:03:50,484
I went all over Vienna...

1124
01:03:50,485 --> 01:03:52,405
looking for the right
coffee shop to buy it.

1125
01:03:52,925 --> 01:03:55,018
Wandering in the sun.

1126
01:03:55,241 --> 01:03:57,137
Did not you have the car?

1127
01:03:57,967 --> 01:04:01,431
Do you think I would use the Baron's
car for my personal affairs?

1128
01:04:02,014 --> 01:04:03,878
And I found a beauty.

1129
01:04:04,948 --> 01:04:07,010
Black marble tables.

1130
01:04:07,011 --> 01:04:09,822
Red plush furniture,
golden mirrors.

1131
01:04:09,942 --> 01:04:12,121
It was the most beautiful cafe in Vienna.

1132
01:04:12,955 --> 01:04:14,754
We could make a fortune.

1133
01:04:14,755 --> 01:04:16,467
Here it is, Karl.

1134
01:04:20,482 --> 01:04:21,911
Sophie, you offend me.

1135
01:04:23,719 --> 01:04:26,888
Thinking of money right now.

1136
01:04:34,160 --> 01:04:35,654
<i>DOMESTIC HOUSES.</i>

1137
01:04:35,689 --> 01:04:36,689
<i>For hunting the boar</i>

1138
01:04:36,817 --> 01:04:40,955
<i>47 horses ready at dawn
Hunting lunch for 50 guests.</i>

1139
01:04:42,892 --> 01:04:44,437
Hurry with those pigeons.

1140
01:04:47,908 --> 01:04:49,348
These lobsters are ready.

1141
01:04:49,349 --> 01:04:51,118
Better send them up.

1142
01:04:52,279 --> 01:04:54,904
Hey, what's up with that oven?

1143
01:04:56,289 --> 01:04:57,526
And Anna...

1144
01:04:57,528 --> 01:05:00,335
tell Otto to take three
bottles of Brandy Napoleon.

1145
01:05:02,738 --> 01:05:04,258
It does not have the necessary height.

1146
01:05:04,397 --> 01:05:05,626
It is four inches tall.

1147
01:05:05,627 --> 01:05:06,669
It does not have the necessary height.

1148
01:05:06,670 --> 01:05:08,000
Why do you say that?

1149
01:05:08,001 --> 01:05:09,967
It's not high enough for this house.

1150
01:05:09,968 --> 01:05:12,665
I've been working in
this house for 20 years.

1151
01:05:15,442 --> 01:05:17,963
Hey, do you want to shut up, you parrots?!

1152
01:05:17,964 --> 01:05:21,063
44... 46... 48... 50.

1153
01:05:21,064 --> 01:05:22,064
Shut up!

1154
01:05:24,115 --> 01:05:25,508
56... 58...

1155
01:05:25,646 --> 01:05:28,576
60... 65... 100.

1156
01:05:53,140 --> 01:05:55,828
What time is the fastest
train to Paris?

1157
01:07:06,488 --> 01:07:07,488
Otto.

1158
01:07:10,221 --> 01:07:13,490
Three bottles of Napoleon Brandy.

1159
01:07:14,666 --> 01:07:15,666
What?

1160
01:07:15,693 --> 01:07:19,415
Three bottles of Napoleon
Brandy, up here.

1161
01:07:25,368 --> 01:07:25,868
Anna

1162
01:07:26,142 --> 01:07:27,777
I've been looking for
you all over the house.

1163
01:07:27,778 --> 01:07:29,655
Karl, let me go. I'm scared.

1164
01:07:29,656 --> 01:07:30,991
Oh, well, it's normal that you're scared.

1165
01:07:30,992 --> 01:07:32,378
You do not have to come down.

1166
01:07:32,379 --> 01:07:33,391
Look, charm.

1167
01:07:33,392 --> 01:07:34,751
I have not forgotten you.

1168
01:07:34,752 --> 01:07:36,767
I was just waiting for
my plans to be ready.

1169
01:07:37,093 --> 01:07:39,008
There is a train leaving
Vienna in one hour.

1170
01:07:39,009 --> 01:07:40,016
Think about it.

1171
01:07:40,017 --> 01:07:41,399
Karl! Karl, please!

1172
01:07:41,400 --> 01:07:42,860
I love Albert.

1173
01:07:43,031 --> 01:07:44,882
It's a bit late for you to
think about that, right?

1174
01:07:44,883 --> 01:07:46,464
Let's finish with this nonsense.

1175
01:07:46,863 --> 01:07:48,711
We are crazy for each other.

1176
01:07:48,723 --> 01:07:49,518
And you know.

1177
01:07:49,519 --> 01:07:50,875
Let's go somewhere...

1178
01:07:50,876 --> 01:07:52,662
before you have the
chance to tell him.

1179
01:07:52,663 --> 01:07:54,498
You love Me. You love Me!

1180
01:07:54,505 --> 01:07:55,565
No no. Karl.

1181
01:07:55,572 --> 01:07:57,858
All I want is my
husband and my job.

1182
01:07:57,859 --> 01:07:59,339
Let me go, please!

1183
01:07:59,340 --> 01:08:00,539
Listen out.

1184
01:08:00,540 --> 01:08:02,079
Are you going to do what
I say and come with me?

1185
01:08:02,080 --> 01:08:03,835
Or are you going to be
around until you get kicked?

1186
01:08:03,836 --> 01:08:05,655
Please, have a little mercy.

1187
01:08:05,667 --> 01:08:07,808
Piety? I tell you...

1188
01:08:08,660 --> 01:08:10,051
I love you.

1189
01:08:10,259 --> 01:08:11,725
Listen, Anna...

1190
01:08:11,726 --> 01:08:13,477
I have much money to spend.

1191
01:08:13,478 --> 01:08:15,121
We will spend like kings.

1192
01:08:15,122 --> 01:08:17,080
I'm going to make you happy.

1193
01:08:17,081 --> 01:08:18,243
It's Sophie's money.

1194
01:08:18,244 --> 01:08:20,255
And what else does it give you?
I'm going to spend it with you.

1195
01:08:20,264 --> 01:08:21,926
- Spending Sophie's money with me?
- Yes.

1196
01:08:21,927 --> 01:08:23,953
No, I will not go with you!
I will not go!

1197
01:08:23,954 --> 01:08:24,954
Oh, listen!

1198
01:08:25,064 --> 01:08:27,058
I will leave you here for
nothing in the world.

1199
01:08:27,063 --> 01:08:28,315
You are welcome!

1200
01:08:28,316 --> 01:08:30,364
Besides, how do you know Albert
wants you to stay here...

1201
01:08:30,365 --> 01:08:31,832
once you know what's ours?

1202
01:08:31,833 --> 01:08:33,456
And he will know because I will tell him!

1203
01:08:33,457 --> 01:08:35,008
- Oh no!
- Oh yeah!

1204
01:08:35,009 --> 01:08:37,025
And to each inhabitant of this house.

1205
01:08:37,544 --> 01:08:39,758
If Albert does not have
arrests to forgive you,

1206
01:08:39,759 --> 01:08:41,838
the others will make your life impossible.

1207
01:08:41,839 --> 01:08:43,516
You will not be able to
continue living here!

1208
01:08:43,517 --> 01:08:45,200
Let go of me, you filthy beast!

1209
01:08:45,764 --> 01:08:47,465
So you do not want to leave, huh?

1210
01:08:47,466 --> 01:08:48,907
All right, then
I'll tell Albert!

1211
01:08:48,908 --> 01:08:51,200
I'll tell him and he'll kick you out!

1212
01:08:51,446 --> 01:08:53,514
Come here! Come here!
Give me that!

1213
01:08:55,090 --> 01:08:55,906
Give me that!

1214
01:08:55,977 --> 01:08:57,280
Do not!

1215
01:09:04,383 --> 01:09:06,492
I'll see what happens.

1216
01:09:26,991 --> 01:09:27,963
Albert, I'm sorry.

1217
01:09:27,964 --> 01:09:29,999
The barrel slid and
hit the wine rack.

1218
01:09:30,847 --> 01:09:32,013
As a...

1219
01:09:32,153 --> 01:09:33,346
Albert!

1220
01:09:34,592 --> 01:09:35,498
Albert!

1221
01:09:35,510 --> 01:09:36,510
Do not!

1222
01:09:37,161 --> 01:09:38,184
Albert!

1223
01:09:42,565 --> 01:09:44,027
I'm sorry Mr.

1224
01:09:44,454 --> 01:09:48,127
But many of its best
bottles have been broken.

1225
01:09:48,593 --> 01:09:49,738
I lost my head.

1226
01:09:49,739 --> 01:09:52,470
The spilled wine is not
as important as this.

1227
01:09:53,269 --> 01:09:55,057
Yes sir. I am sorry.

1228
01:09:55,070 --> 01:09:56,851
Go back to work
and fix the mess.

1229
01:09:56,852 --> 01:09:58,071
I do not want to know anything
else about the matter.

1230
01:09:58,072 --> 01:09:59,308
Yes sir.

1231
01:10:02,877 --> 01:10:04,841
You, go back to work!

1232
01:10:05,148 --> 01:10:06,851
And help clean the cellar.

1233
01:10:19,134 --> 01:10:21,076
Leave this place clean.

1234
01:10:27,068 --> 01:10:29,399
Liebfrauenmilch!

1235
01:10:37,061 --> 01:10:38,324
Well, Karl.

1236
01:10:38,797 --> 01:10:40,566
I think I rushed.

1237
01:10:46,807 --> 01:10:49,175
Anna, it's better to go
up and change clothes.

1238
01:10:49,617 --> 01:10:51,050
And Franz...

1239
01:10:51,051 --> 01:10:52,520
you and Ernst go back to the kitchen.

1240
01:10:52,521 --> 01:10:54,149
We will finish this tomorrow.

1241
01:10:56,372 --> 01:10:58,306
No, Karl, do not go.

1242
01:10:58,547 --> 01:11:00,191
You are still nervous.

1243
01:11:00,530 --> 01:11:02,680
I'm sorry, I lost my composure.

1244
01:11:03,080 --> 01:11:05,529
It is not the way to fix things.

1245
01:11:06,696 --> 01:11:08,586
Better take something.

1246
01:11:09,832 --> 01:11:10,845
Clear.

1247
01:11:15,386 --> 01:11:16,865
Here is one that is not broken.

1248
01:11:18,387 --> 01:11:20,330
Intact, Karl.

1249
01:11:21,952 --> 01:11:23,328
But affected.

1250
01:11:25,191 --> 01:11:26,920
The wine is like that.

1251
01:11:27,120 --> 01:11:28,832
Easily alterable.

1252
01:11:29,179 --> 01:11:30,602
Like a woman.

1253
01:11:34,847 --> 01:11:38,056
And when she's upset, she
needs time to calm down.

1254
01:11:39,763 --> 01:11:43,232
Time for the grounds to
return to the bottom.

1255
01:11:49,595 --> 01:11:54,711
With some care, time and rest,
you will get well again.

1256
01:11:55,551 --> 01:11:58,102
But you must take care of the wine.

1257
01:11:59,569 --> 01:12:01,227
And of women.

1258
01:12:03,265 --> 01:12:05,805
Otto, stay in the care of wine.

1259
01:12:06,998 --> 01:12:08,247
And of the women...?

1260
01:12:09,445 --> 01:12:10,540
Good...

1261
01:12:11,813 --> 01:12:13,501
It is a work of men.

1262
01:12:14,635 --> 01:12:16,316
Take care of them.

1263
01:12:18,170 --> 01:12:19,803
A few glasses, Otto.

1264
01:12:21,825 --> 01:12:23,425
I'm sorry about what happened, Albert.

1265
01:12:23,426 --> 01:12:26,955
I imagine it's too late to
cry for the spilled wine.

1266
01:12:28,152 --> 01:12:29,505
It is done.

1267
01:12:30,645 --> 01:12:32,408
Let's have a drink, huh?

1268
01:12:33,568 --> 01:12:35,020
Oh no.

1269
01:12:35,300 --> 01:12:37,331
We will provide something special.

1270
01:12:39,111 --> 01:12:40,550
I will bring a bottle.

1271
01:12:54,590 --> 01:12:56,124
Hey, I do not want wine.

1272
01:12:57,009 --> 01:12:58,255
Blind?

1273
01:12:58,256 --> 01:13:00,189
Do not. I'm not blind

1274
01:13:00,327 --> 01:13:02,026
I'm just deaf

1275
01:13:02,027 --> 01:13:03,228
I do not hear.

1276
01:13:08,147 --> 01:13:09,391
Here we are.

1277
01:13:22,536 --> 01:13:23,759
Well, Karl.

1278
01:13:24,346 --> 01:13:25,911
For your future!

1279
01:13:27,396 --> 01:13:29,029
And no more spilled wine.

1280
01:13:35,492 --> 01:13:37,536
Well, Albert, I
accepted your apology.

1281
01:13:37,537 --> 01:13:38,959
I think now I should go.

1282
01:13:38,960 --> 01:13:40,181
Yes, Karl.

1283
01:13:40,740 --> 01:13:43,119
Ten minutes to collect
your stuff and get away!

1284
01:13:43,120 --> 01:13:44,647
Take my hands off!

1285
01:13:45,577 --> 01:13:47,822
Now we will do it without making a fuss!

1286
01:13:48,106 --> 01:13:50,245
I could have killed you if
the Baron does not stop me.

1287
01:13:50,246 --> 01:13:52,880
Oh, save my life so you
could fire me, huh?

1288
01:13:53,070 --> 01:13:54,365
Well, do not kid yourself, Albert.

1289
01:13:54,366 --> 01:13:56,233
If you want to get out
of here in 10 minutes,

1290
01:13:56,240 --> 01:13:58,117
You will have to work quickly.

1291
01:13:58,123 --> 01:13:59,002
Hears...

1292
01:13:59,003 --> 01:14:00,998
I will be here
as long as I want.

1293
01:14:00,999 --> 01:14:02,719
And you're going to have to put up with it.

1294
01:14:02,976 --> 01:14:06,322
Out of my sight or I can not
take your hands off you.

1295
01:14:06,625 --> 01:14:08,027
You're going to take my hands off me

1296
01:14:08,028 --> 01:14:10,048
because the people from
above will tell you.

1297
01:14:10,049 --> 01:14:10,997
If you say goodbye again,

1298
01:14:11,023 --> 01:14:12,750
I will turn you into a laughingstock again.

1299
01:14:12,798 --> 01:14:15,219
And those above will
do what I tell them.

1300
01:14:15,220 --> 01:14:16,189
No, Karl!

1301
01:14:16,190 --> 01:14:18,589
You will never be near the ones above.

1302
01:14:18,590 --> 01:14:19,787
You are done.

1303
01:14:20,319 --> 01:14:21,746
Leave the Baroness out of this.

1304
01:14:21,747 --> 01:14:23,350
And to Sophie, leave her alone.

1305
01:14:23,351 --> 01:14:24,934
I have everything I need from Sophie.

1306
01:14:24,935 --> 01:14:25,804
And my wife...

1307
01:14:25,805 --> 01:14:27,545
You're going to save them all, right?

1308
01:14:27,546 --> 01:14:28,975
Well, look.

1309
01:14:29,110 --> 01:14:31,215
When they're over, I'll
go for the Baroness's.

1310
01:14:31,216 --> 01:14:33,254
And she'll pay me until I want to.

1311
01:14:35,392 --> 01:14:37,209
Filthy pig!

1312
01:14:39,097 --> 01:14:40,874
So there's no other
option with you?

1313
01:14:41,314 --> 01:14:43,815
My wife can not protect herself from you?

1314
01:14:44,341 --> 01:14:45,240
Come on, let's go!

1315
01:14:45,247 --> 01:14:48,095
Stand up and fight, dirty rat!

1316
01:14:48,096 --> 01:14:50,011
I give you that opportunity.

1317
01:14:50,012 --> 01:14:52,793
But only one will come out on its own.

1318
01:14:52,794 --> 01:14:56,676
No, damn dog!

1319
01:15:00,219 --> 01:15:01,093
Albert!

1320
01:15:01,094 --> 01:15:02,151
Albert, stop!

1321
01:15:02,152 --> 01:15:03,418
You are killing him!

1322
01:15:06,842 --> 01:15:09,199
Call the Baron!
It is killing you!

1323
01:15:10,801 --> 01:15:11,844
Albert!

1324
01:15:12,043 --> 01:15:12,800
Albert!

1325
01:15:12,961 --> 01:15:14,688
Take this!

1326
01:15:14,897 --> 01:15:15,993
Albert!

1327
01:15:20,340 --> 01:15:22,069
Come on, get up!

1328
01:15:22,289 --> 01:15:23,424
Come on!

1329
01:15:30,815 --> 01:15:32,255
Quick! Quick!

1330
01:15:32,281 --> 01:15:33,342
It is killing you.

1331
01:15:35,180 --> 01:15:36,000
Albert!

1332
01:15:36,100 --> 01:15:37,383
For! Enough is enough!

1333
01:15:37,446 --> 01:15:38,848
I will take care of this.

1334
01:15:38,962 --> 01:15:40,951
Excuse me sir...

1335
01:15:40,952 --> 01:15:42,517
but this time I will do it.

1336
01:15:43,429 --> 01:15:45,250
He has something to tell you.

1337
01:15:45,526 --> 01:15:47,529
Some twisted idea.

1338
01:15:48,310 --> 01:15:49,663
Come on, let's go!

1339
01:15:49,664 --> 01:15:51,169
Say it!

1340
01:15:51,524 --> 01:15:52,973
Nothing, Lord.

1341
01:15:53,681 --> 01:15:55,110
Sophie, come here!

1342
01:15:55,957 --> 01:15:58,142
Give him back the money you
stole from this woman.

1343
01:15:59,090 --> 01:16:00,249
Come on!

1344
01:16:04,358 --> 01:16:05,603
And my wife.

1345
01:16:06,165 --> 01:16:07,883
There is something pending with her.

1346
01:16:08,407 --> 01:16:09,925
Come on. Tell her!

1347
01:16:10,471 --> 01:16:12,253
Say it! Come on.

1348
01:16:12,254 --> 01:16:13,142
Nothing.

1349
01:16:13,143 --> 01:16:14,775
Creepy!

1350
01:16:15,089 --> 01:16:16,783
Out of here!

1351
01:16:21,097 --> 01:16:22,723
You loaded my grinder.

1352
01:16:25,048 --> 01:16:26,389
Well done, Albert.

1353
01:16:26,684 --> 01:16:27,825
Thank my Lord.

1354
01:16:28,360 --> 01:16:30,178
Just a little cleaning.

1355
01:16:30,551 --> 01:16:32,676
Go back to work. Everybody!

1356
01:16:32,677 --> 01:16:34,666
As before. Hurry!

1357
01:16:35,236 --> 01:16:36,300
Very good, Albert.

1358
01:16:36,301 --> 01:16:37,471
Thank my Lord.

1359
01:16:39,207 --> 01:16:40,180
What did he say, Albert?

1360
01:16:40,181 --> 01:16:41,642
Nothing sweetheart.

1361
01:16:41,808 --> 01:16:43,956
Everything is well now.
Do not worry.

1362
01:16:43,957 --> 01:16:45,239
Yes sir.

1363
01:16:46,352 --> 01:16:48,531
Did not I tell you not to call me "Sir"?

1364
01:16:48,532 --> 01:16:49,728
Yes sir.

1365
01:16:50,131 --> 01:16:51,783
Well, just one more, ma'am.

1366
01:16:51,784 --> 01:16:54,989
Oh, no, no, Olly.
I will not interview more drivers today.

1367
01:16:55,196 --> 01:16:57,509
Tomorrow afternoon at three.

1368
01:17:10,753 --> 01:17:11,460
And good?

1369
01:17:11,461 --> 01:17:13,026
The new chauffeur of the Lady.

1370
01:17:13,326 --> 01:17:14,349
I hope so.

